videos.headline: Things getting testy between Miami and FSU
videos.description: Miami and Florida State's rivalry is on full display in Tallahassee.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Things getting testy between Miami and FSU) 2019/11/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Dallas slices his way through FSU's defense
videos.description: Miami's DeeJay Dallas breaks away for a 42-yard gain off the screen pass against Florida State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Dallas slices his way through FSU's defense) 2019/11/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Thomas beats defender for 39-yard Miami TD
videos.description: Jeff Thomas beats the safety for a 39-yard touchdown, putting Miami on the board 7-0 against Florida State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Thomas beats defender for 39-yard Miami TD) 2019/11/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Terry gets up high for a 20-yard grab
videos.description: Florida State's Alex Hornibrook evades the pressure and hits Tamorrion Terry for the 20-yard gain.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Terry gets up high for a 20-yard grab) 2019/11/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: FSU's defense forces turnover
videos.description: Florida State's defense gets the turnover off of a strip sack on Miami QB Jarren Williams.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (FSU's defense forces turnover) 2019/11/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Williams finds Harley for 34-yard Miami gain
videos.description: Jarren Williams puts Miami in the redzone after hitting Mike Harley on the corner route for a 34-yard reception.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Williams finds Harley for 34-yard Miami gain) 2019/11/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Dallas' rushing TD extends lead for Miami
videos.description: Miami's DeeJay Dallas goes full steam ahead into the end zone for his first touchdown of the day.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Dallas' rushing TD extends lead for Miami) 2019/11/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Akers tip toes his way into end zone
videos.description: Alex Hornibrook dumps it off to Cam Akers for the 18-yard touchdown, cutting the deficit to 17-10 against Miami.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Akers tip toes his way into end zone) 2019/11/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bolden injures himself celebrating INT
videos.description: Miami's Bubba Bolden gets the interception but pays the price after colliding with his own teammate.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Bolden injures himself celebrating INT) 2019/11/02 ESHEET
